name: Logic & Last Resort - True Talk - CD
description:
Overstand Music proudly presents it’s first release – True Talk, by acclaimed People’s Army rapper Logic & producer Last Resort.  With guest features including the likes of Maverick Sabre, Klashnekoff, Lowkey, Akala, Shadia Mansour and more, the album has already been hailed as a UK Hip Hop classic.  Essential listening!

name: Overstand Samples Vol 1. - Last Resort - CD
description:
Exclusively available in the Overstand Shop, we proudly present the first of our sample CD series.  For producers of all experiences, Last Resort presents a fantastic selection of drums and breakbeats, royalty free to use in your own projects.  Many of the sounds have been used in tracks featuring the likes of Logic, Klashnekoff, Lowkey, Maverick Sabre, Akala, Shadia Mansour and many more!

Last Resort – Overstand Sample CD Vol 1. includes the following sounds and samples in high quality 24bit WAV format:

50 x Original Last Resort processed drum loops

1x bonus pack containing a small selection of single hit kicks, snares and hats from the next forthcoming pack in the series
